The paper discusses the impact of big data on society and proposes a research roadmap for Europe to optimize its use. The paper covers various topics related to data management, processing, analytics, protection, and visualization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CY (Computers and Society), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
